 *	2 - MOD_RIFLE_BULLET
 *	3 - MOD_PROJECTILE
 *	4 - MOD_PROJECTILE_SPLASH
 *	5 - MOD_EXPLOSIVE
 *	6 - MOD_EXPLOSIVE_SPLASH
 *	7 - MOD_GRENADE
 *	8 - MOD_GRENADE_SPLASH
 *
 *	Flags that are set at the end of paths
 *	0. start_be_1
 *	1. complete_be_1
